argin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;时刻保持警觉的心灵</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;发现人类能力的极大可能性</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><br/></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt; 你该来听 &lt;&lt;</span></h2><p><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;">&nbsp; ●&nbsp; 西方哲学爱好者</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;●&nbsp; 萨特、加缪的追随者• 面对复杂人生、太多选择的困惑者</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;