第十二讲 | 萨特：被自由绑架

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/app8SohzMGQ4020/a_5c4ab785d5e5d_4sQJ1ABS

<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/13250900_1545363433.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="存在-04.jpg" style="text-align: center;" class="loadingclass"/><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">人的存在意味着什么？人应该如何度过一生？生命必须要有一个意义吗？</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">存在主义哲学关注的恰恰就是生命中最重要、最个人化的问题并提供思路：</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">我们是谁？为什么我们是现在这个样子？</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">自由是什么？如何做选择？</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">自我与他人是如何互动的？如果我们不信仰上帝，我们能否找到生命的意义？</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">我们想要创造一个什么样的世界？</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">我们需要承担什么样的责任？我们要做什么？</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">存在主义诞生于一战后支离破碎、信仰缺失的欧洲，</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">为千百万失去信仰的年轻人提供了人生观与价值观。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">存在主义关于自由和叛逆的思想深刻的融入流行文化，</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">并为女权主义、同性恋权利、阶级壁垒的瓦解、反种族主义和反殖民斗争提供了强大的理论武器，最终从根本上改变了我们今天的生存基础。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">伴随着科技进步和经济的飞速发展，</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">被生活裹挟的现代人，</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">面对世事无常、深度丧失、悲喜剧交替上演、生命意义难寻的生存境遇，像浮萍一般漂浮在各种各样的可能性之间，充满了焦虑和寂寞。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">而存在主义将引导我们，在真实的人生处境中，用行动不断寻找自我存在的价值，同时让我们学会为自己的人生负起责任。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">我们比想象中更自由，更需要意义，也更需要存在主义。</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/51406300_1545363433.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="存在-06.jpg" class="loadingclass"/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: left; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: left; white-space: normal;"><br/></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt; 10个与现代生活息息相关的重大问题 &lt;&lt;</span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">存在主义给出最严肃也最乐观的</span></h2><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/85170500_1545363433.jpg" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px;" class="loadingclass"/><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: left; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br/></span></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt; 你将获得 &lt;&lt;</span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><br/></h2><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp; ● &nbsp;5位存在主义大师的哲学思想精华</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;●&nbsp; 一种解决人生关键问题的思路</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;●&nbsp; 现代西方哲学思想发展趋势的洞悉</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp; ●&nbsp; 解放自我与天性的一次尝试</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;对人性与命运的深入理解</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;塑造崭新的生活方式或生活态度的尝试</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;时刻保持警觉的心灵</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;发现人类能力的极大可能性</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><br/></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt; 你该来听 &lt;&lt;</span></h2><p><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;">&nbsp; ●&nbsp; 西方哲学爱好者</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;●&nbsp; 萨特、加缪的追随者• 面对复杂人生、太多选择的困惑者</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;